               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430703-name-512" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430703-name-512" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430703-name-512" type="surname" value="FULCHER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430703-name-512" type="given" value="SAMUEL JOHN"></interp>SAMUEL JOHN FULCHER.</persName>
                  </hi> I live in Wilmott-street, Bethnal-green. The prisoner had been my apprentice, but his time had expired, and I discharged him—I saw this property safe in one of my drawers about the 2nd of June, and I missed it about the 11th—they are my son's property—my wife ab<lb></lb>sconded, and went to the prisoner—my daughter went to where the prisoner worked, in Hare-street, and found him at work.</p>
