               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I bought the trowsers on the 2nd of May; the hand<lb></lb>kerchiefs</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184307030056"></xptr>
               <p>and waistcoat I had about a fortnight before his mother came;—she and my aunt went to Stepney fair, and asked me to go; she said she would sooner go to the bottom of the canal than go home any more.</p>
